27:06.733 --> 27:11.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARCIA BIGGS: It starts at dawn
here in West Mosul, members
of Iraqi special forces going

27:13.100 --> 27:17.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
