turned his house into a jail.

27:40.233 --> 27:45.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ISIS imprisoned anyone
who didn't pledge loyalty
to them, who didn't
join them and stick to

27:45.000 --> 27:47.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
