lieutenant says.

27:47.266 --> 27:50.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They considered them outlaws.

27:50.533 --> 27:55.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
After several hours searching,
they come across this man, who
they believe may have escaped

27:55.266 --> 27:57.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the current clashes
in the Old City.

27:57.633 --> 27:59.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
