28:08.300 --> 28:10.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
No one has ever seen here.

28:10.100 --> 28:11.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
People here don't know him.

28:11.333 --> 28:13.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He is very thin, and
the I.D. card is fake.

28:13.400 --> 28:15.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
