28:15.600 --> 28:20.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator):
For no reason, the militias
took my son five months ago.

28:33.133 --> 28:34.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We don't know where.

28:34.133 --> 28:35.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
We are not ISIS.

28:35.633 --> 28:37.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
My son is a shepherd.

28:37.166 --> 28:39.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
If we were ISIS, you
could come and kill me.

28:39.333 --> 28:44.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Ask anyone here.

28:50.433 --> 28:55.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
