42:38.666 --> 42:43.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: We have
known about the dangers of
hard hits and concussions from

42:43.200 --> 42:48.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
football, and that many
players are suffering
from CTE, or chronic
traumatic encephalopathy.

42:50.233 --> 42:53.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
