their brains had CTE.

43:01.033 --> 43:05.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
These included former
greats such as quarterback
Kenny Stabler and
linebacker Dave Duerson.

43:05.800 --> 43:10.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Researchers also looked at the
brains of 202 former players,
including high school and

43:12.200 --> 43:16.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
