in terms of risk for CTE.

46:32.066 --> 46:34.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We did find it in
three individuals.

46:34.600 --> 46:39.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we need to, you know,
identify those people
