46:41.100 --> 46:44.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Speaking of
that, while this is obviously
the gold standard, you have

46:44.233 --> 46:47.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
